name: Associative_7
latex: {\displaystyle \left.{\begin{matrix}(A\cap B)\cap C=A\cap (B\cap C)=A\cap B\cap C\quad \\(A\cup B)\cup C=A\cup (B\cup C)=A\cup B\cup C\quad \end{matrix}}\right\}{\mbox{for all sets }}A,B,C.}

name: Associative_8
latex: {\displaystyle (f\circ g)\circ h=f\circ (g\circ h)=f\circ g\circ h\qquad {\mbox{for all }}f,g,h\in S.}
